- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper deals with cyber-physical systems and their dynamics. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper mentions computation and control in modern applications. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is another possibility as the paper deals with distributed systems. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper mentions collision freedom in distributed car control.
